         <abstract>
            <p>Filippi [1] has proposed a quadrature scheme for any function f(x) in [ -1, 1 ], based on expanding the integrand in a series of Chebyshev polynomials of the second kind. In this paper the error associated with this quadrature method when applied to analytic functions has been investigated in detail.</p>
          </abstract>
